      "blurb": "docs/agents/* — the bindings that make ticket, label, and change request real nouns here."
    },
    {
      "id": "setup",
      "title": "Setup & shipped templates",
      "blurb": "backlog setup writes and reconciles the playbooks from these baselines."
    }
